        <updateDate>2009-03-04T18:56:23Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Deficit Accountability Act of 2009 - Amends the Legislative Reorganization Act of 1946 to provide that pay for Members of Congress may not be increased by any adjustment scheduled to take effect in a calendar year if the Office of Management and Budget (OMB) determines there was a deficit in the preceding fiscal year.]]></text>
      </summary>
